        "TileImage": "$($repository 6f89886b-ac8a-4828-bc04-6e314ded5c28).Image",
        "Description": "A Hitman is contracted to eliminate three mechanics. The Hitman approached them several times, but they stuck together never giving the Hitman an opening. Then one day the mechanics had an argument and separated from each another. The Hitman could now simply pick them off one at a time. A task he proceeded with do with gusto.\r\r&quot;In unity is strength.&quot;",
